headline: Principal® names Deanna Strable next president and CEO
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa, November 12, 2024--Principal Financial Group® (Nasdaq: PFG) today announced the Board of Directors has appointed president and chief operating officer Deanna Strable as the company’s next president and chief executive officer, effective January 7, 2025. Strable succeeds Dan Houston, who will continue to serve as executive chair of the Board.
